      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The exterior features a vibrant paint finish, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small door ding on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
